    <j.0:dossier_title xml:lang="en">Proposal for a COUNCIL DECISION on the position to be taken on behalf of the European Union at the third meeting of the Conference of the Parties to the Minamata Convention on Mercury as regards the adoption of a Decision on the phasing-out of dental amalgam and amending Annex A to this Convention</j.0:dossier_title>
